                            java.lang.String name,
                            java.lang.String externalId,
                            java.lang.String externalSystem,
                            java.lang.String publish,
                            java.lang.String navigate)
        Creates the Collection section.
        Parameters:
        collectionId - The record ID of the shared metadata record in Rosetta tables
        collectionParentId - The Parent Object Record ID
        name - name
        externalId - The unique identifier of the collection
        externalSystem - The name of the ILS that the collection is originated from.
        publish - Used to mark the Collections to be published
        navigate - The ability to navigate to the collection from its sub collections
